 <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-719">使用者需要測試傳回的型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-719">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-720">例如，套用至物件的</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-720">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-721">執行 XML 結構描述驗證時，如果`XmlSchemaType`或`XmlSchemaDatatype`對應至所讀取的目前項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-721">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-722">如果正在執行文件類型定義 （DTD 驗證），則這個屬性會傳回`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-722">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` 會傳回目前的項目或屬性，如果是簡單類型，可以指定的簡單型別，例如最小和最大的特殊的驗證條件約束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` 會傳回目前的項目或屬性，如果是使用者定義的簡單型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` 會傳回目前的項目是否使用者定義的 complexType。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-726">此類型不能傳回屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-726">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-727">如果<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A>byla nastavena ValidationType.None，為了從結構描述或 Dtd 提供任何資料型別資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-727">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="38c8e-728">之後呼叫<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>，SchemaType 將會傳回 Null。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38c8e-728">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
